### Test Payslip API Endpoints

# Base URL - Update this to your actual API URL
@baseUrl = https://localhost:7000

### 1. Get Total Hours Worked for Staff (with specific week)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payslip/totalhoursworked/1?weekStartDate=2024-01-15

### 2. Get Total Hours Worked for Staff (current week)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payslip/totalhoursworked/1

### 3. Create New Payslip
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payslip/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "StaffId": 1,
    "WeekStartDate": "2024-01-15T00:00:00"
}

### 4. Get All Payslips
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payslip

### 5. Get Payslips by Staff ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payslip/staff/1

### 6. Delete Payslip by ID
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/api/payslip/1

### 7. Test with different staff ID
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payslip/totalhoursworked/2?weekStartDate=2024-01-15

### 8. Create Payslip for Staff ID 2
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/payslip/create
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "StaffId": 2,
    "WeekStartDate": "2024-01-15T00:00:00"
}

### 9. Get Payslips for Staff ID 2
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/payslip/staff/2
